{"tid":502582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"環團做野! AQI指標引爆環團不滿 政府悄改定義造成民眾混淆","createTime":"2017-12-18T04:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T05:48:22.000Z","uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"663f24e56e7158dac20b19197768e0480400ce18","tid":502582,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T04:56:42.000Z","msg":"【檢視空污】AQI指標引爆環團不滿　環署悄改定義造成民眾混淆<br />\n2017/12/17 15:49<br />\n<br />\n台灣在2012年才訂定PM2.5管制規範標準，並和原本的PSI空氣品質指標並行幾年，去年才整合兩指標，並納入臭氧8小時成為現在的AQI，卻也成了部分環團與環保署爭執的引爆點，環團痛批將環署原本PM2.5指標代表空污不良的「紫爆」弄不見，環署則強調是將空污不良的標準下修。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171217/1261128/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171217%2F1261128%2F&d=bGNBR22iDGm65AEqoHDsIE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bc19f439\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171217%2F1261128%2F&h=c4031f51\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171217/1261128/</a><br />\n<br />\n傻豬唔係香港呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無民主係差啲架啦 <br />\n監察政府既權都無埋"},{"pid":"d8e1b3667c5df800871af00ed8d2c10dffc54c7c","tid":502582,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"香港早幾年已經由歐洲標準改支那標準啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2914637a33f7fac2169b5810582395abb19171a","tid":502582,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港早幾年已經由歐洲標準改支那標準啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}